note: I was born on October 16, 1958 in Buffalo, New York City to Samuel Edward and Matilda West. At various points, my father worked as a funeral home owner, an insurance salesman, and as a porter on the Baltimore and Ohio Railroad. My mother was a school teacher and worked at Langley Air Force Base during World War II. I have one brother, Nathaniel. graduating from George P. Phoenix High School, Later went on to attend Hampton University in Virginia with plans of attending medical school.
